sub_title: Executive senior professional with a strong background in geology and maritime information technology.
summary: Experienced professional who built an organisation to international success. At the moment enjoying time to reflect and orient on future endeavours, building on past experiences and achievements. Broad interest in various sectors ranging from Maritime Information Technology, innovative waste management, renewable energy and circular economy, culture and archeology, mentoring and education. Driven and committed people person; enjoying cycling and hiking; (arthouse) movies; visiting musea, concerts and reading (Salomon Kroonenberg, Jared Diamond).
